---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Amplified Generative AI Innovation Center">
	<Header />
	
	<main class="pt-16 lg:pt-20">
		<!-- Hero Section -->
		<section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 py-20">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
				<h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
					Your privacy is important to us. This policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.
				</p>
				<div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">
					Last updated: December 2024
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
		<section class="py-20 bg-white">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
				<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
					
					<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-50 to-orange-50 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-amber-500 mb-12">
						<h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Quick Summary</h2>
						<p class="text-gray-700">
							We collect minimal information to provide our services, never sell your data, and are committed to transparency about our practices. Your privacy and data security are our top priorities.
						</p>
					</div>

					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">1. Information We Collect</h2>
					
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Information You Provide</h3>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
						<li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and organization when you contact us or register for our programs</li>
						<li><strong>Professional Information:</strong> Job title, industry, and professional interests when relevant to our services</li>
						<li><strong>Communication Content:</strong> Messages, questions, and feedback you send to us</li>
						<li><strong>Research Participation:</strong> Data you provide when participating in our research studies (with explicit consent)</li>
					</ul>

					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Information We Collect Automatically</h3>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
						<li><strong>Website Usage:</strong> Pages visited, time spent, and navigation patterns on our website</li>
						<li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Browser type, operating system, and IP address</li>
						<li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Small files stored on your device to improve your experience (see Cookie Policy below)</li>
					</ul>

					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
					
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
						<div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
							<h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Core Services</h4>
							<ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
								<li>• Respond to your inquiries</li>
								<li>• Provide requested information</li>
								<li>• Process applications</li>
								<li>• Deliver training programs</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
						<div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
							<h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Communications</h4>
							<ul class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1">
								<li>• Send newsletters (with consent)</li>
								<li>• Share research updates</li>
								<li>• Notify about events</li>
								<li>• Provide support</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>

					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">3. Information Sharing</h2>
					
					<div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-200 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
						<h4 class="font-bold text-red-800 mb-3">We DO NOT:</h4>
						<ul class="text-red-700 space-y-1">
							<li>• Sell your personal information to third parties</li>
							<li>• Share your data for marketing purposes</li>
							<li>• Provide your information to data brokers</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">We may share information only in these specific cases:</h4>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
						<li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> With trusted partners who help us operate our website and services (e.g., email service providers, analytics tools)</li>
						<li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect our rights and safety</li>
						<li><strong>Research Collaboration:</strong> Anonymized data for legitimate research purposes (with your explicit consent)</li>
						<li><strong>Vanderbilt University:</strong> As part of our institutional affiliation, in accordance with university policies</li>
					</ul>

					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">4. Data Security</h2>
					
					<p class="mb-6">We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your information:</p>
					
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
						<div class="text-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Encryption</h4>
							<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Data encrypted in transit and at rest</p>
						</div>
						<div class="text-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Access Control</h4>
							<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Limited access to authorized personnel</p>
						</div>
						<div class="text-center p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
							<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3">
								<svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
									<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
								</svg>
							</div>
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Regular Monitoring</h4>
							<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Continuous security monitoring and updates</p>
						</div>
					</div>

					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
					
					<div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
						<h4 class="font-bold text-blue-800 mb-3">You have the right to:</h4>
						<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
							<ul class="text-blue-700 space-y-1">
								<li>• Access your personal information</li>
								<li>• Correct inaccurate information</li>
								<li>• Delete your information</li>
								<li>• Opt-out of communications</li>
							</ul>
							<ul class="text-blue-700 space-y-1">
								<li>• Export your data</li>
								<li>• Limit data processing</li>
								<li>• Withdraw consent</li>
								<li>• File a complaint</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>

					<p class="mb-8">To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@amplify.vanderbilt.edu" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">privacy@amplify.vanderbilt.edu</a>. We will respond within 30 days.</p>

					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">6. Cookie Policy</h2>
					
					<p class="mb-4">We use cookies and similar technologies to improve your experience:</p>
					
					<div class="overflow-x-auto mb-8">
						<table class="w-full border-collapse border border-gray-300">
							<thead>
								<tr class="bg-gray-100">
									<th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Cookie Type</th>
									<th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Purpose</th>
									<th class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-left">Required</th>
								</tr>
							</thead>
							<tbody>
								<tr>
									<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 font-medium">Essential</td>
									<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Website functionality and security</td>
									<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-green-600">Yes</td>
								</tr>
								<tr class="bg-gray-50">
									<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 font-medium">Analytics</td>
									<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Understanding website usage and performance</td>
									<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-amber-600">Optional</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 font-medium">Preferences</td>
									<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Remembering your settings and choices</td>
									<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2 text-amber-600">Optional</td>
								</tr>
							</tbody>
						</table>
					</div>

					<p class="mb-8">You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling certain cookies may affect website functionality.</p>

					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">7. Third-Party Services</h2>
					
					<p class="mb-4">We use the following third-party services that may collect information:</p>
					
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
						<li><strong>Coursera:</strong> For online course delivery and enrollment management</li>
						<li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> For website performance analysis (anonymized)</li>
						<li><strong>Email Services:</strong> For communication and newsletter delivery</li>
						<li><strong>Cloud Hosting:</strong> For secure website hosting and data storage</li>
					</ul>

					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">8. International Users</h2>
					
					<p class="mb-8">Our services are primarily intended for users in the United States. If you are accessing our website from outside the US, please be aware that your information may be transferred to and processed in the United States, where our servers are located and our central database is operated.</p>

					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">9. Children's Privacy</h2>
					
					<p class="mb-8">Our services are not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we learn that we have collected such information, we will delete it immediately.</p>

					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
					
					<p class="mb-8">We may update this privacy policy periodically. We will notify you of significant changes by posting a notice on our website or sending an email to registered users. Your continued use of our services after such modifications constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

					<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">11. Contact Information</h2>
					
					<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-purple-50 p-8 rounded-xl">
						<h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Questions about this Privacy Policy?</h4>
						<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
							<div>
								<p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Email:</strong></p>
								<a href="mailto:privacy@amplify.vanderbilt.edu" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">privacy@amplify.vanderbilt.edu</a>
							</div>
							<div>
								<p class="text-gray-700 mb-2"><strong>Mail:</strong></p>
								<address class="text-gray-700 not-italic">
									Amplified Generative AI Innovation Center<br>
									Vanderbilt University<br>
									Nashville, TN 37235<br>
									Attn: Privacy Officer
								</address>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<Footer />
</Layout>